longBusinessSummary: Bokusgruppen AB (publ) operates as a book retailer in Sweden. It offers books, e-books, audio books, games, puzzles, and play and creative creation products. The company also operates bokus.com, an online bookstore; and retail stores under the Akademibokhandeln brand. In addition, it offers Bokus Play, a subscription service for audio and e-books. The company was founded in 1971 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden.
